
Roblox isn't supported on the Steam Deck by the offical Roblox team, but it works pretty well with 3rd party tools.

You will need to install Grapejuice and Flatseal.

This guide has the instructions.

- Reddit [Roblox - Steam Deck guide](https://www.reddit.com/r/SteamDeck/comments/wdf8b3/roblox_steam_deck_guide/)
